FBIS3-54792 "drsov002_m_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-002 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Jan 1994 Tajikistan Chinese Envoy on PRC-Tajik Relations LD0401104394 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1017 GMT 4 Jan 94 LD0401104394 Moscow ITAR-TASS Language: English Article Type:BFN [By KHOVAR-TASS correspondent Valeriy Zhukov] [Text] Dushanbe January 4 TASS -- The second anniversary of diplomatic relations between Tajikitan and China is being marked here today. "This is a major event in the lives of the two nations," Chinese Ambassador Xi Zhaoming told the KHOVAR news service. "Relations between our two countries are being promoted on a sound and perfectly normal basis. Our stands largely coincide in foreign politics." The Chinese diplomat said that there were great potential possibilities for promoting Sino-Tajik cooperation and "this process must be accelerated."
